<span class=\"oo-ui-indicatorElement-indicator oo-ui-indicatorElement-noIndicator\"></span></a></span></div><dl id=\"mwtQ\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><dt id=\"mwtg\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><p class=\"ve-ce-branchNode ve-ce-contentBranchNode ve-ce-paragraphNode ve-ce-generated-wrapper\"><code id=\"mwtw\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-textStyleAnnotation ve-ce-codeAnnotation\">mawk</code></p></dt><dd id=\"mwuA\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><p class=\"ve-ce-branchNode ve-ce-contentBranchNode ve-ce-paragraphNode ve-ce-generated-wrapper\">マイク・ブレナン（<a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%9E\" title=\"英語\" about=\"#mwt154\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;lang-en-short&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Lang-en-short&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;1&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Mike Brennan&quot;}},&quot;i&quot;:0}}]}\" id=\"mwuQ\" class=\"ve-ce-leafNode ve-ce-focusableNode ve-ce-mwTransclusionNode\" contenteditable=\"false\">英</a><span typeof=\"mw:Entity\" about=\"#mwt154\" class=\"ve-ce-leafNode ve-ce-focusableNode ve-ce-mwTransclusionNode\" contenteditable=\"false\">:</span><span about=\"#mwt154\" class=\"ve-ce-leafNode ve-ce-focusableNode ve-ce-mwTransclusionNode\" contenteditable=\"false\"> </span><span lang=\"en\" about=\"#mwt154\" id=\"mwug\" class=\"ve-ce-leafNode ve-ce-focusableNode ve-ce-mwTransclusionNode\" contenteditable=\"false\">Mike Brennan</span>）作。旧版の<code id=\"mwuw\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-textStyleAnnotation ve-ce-codeAnnotation\">awk</code>に少数の拡張が加えられている。<img class=\"ve-ce-nail ve-ce-nail-pre-open\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%90%E3%82%A4%E3%83%88%E3%82%B3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%89\" title=\"バイトコード\" id=\"mwvA\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-nailedAnnotation ve-ce-linkAnnotation ve-ce-mwInternalLinkAnnotation\"><img class=\"ve-ce-nail ve-ce-nail-post-open\">バイトコード<img class=\"ve-ce-nail ve-ce-nail-pre-close\"></a><img class=\"ve-ce-nail ve-ce-nail-post-close\">に変換されて実行されるため，高速な動作が期待できる。また<code id=\"mwvQ\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-textStyleAnnotation ve-ce-codeAnnotation\">gawk</code>よりもバイナリサイズが小さい。</p></dd></dl><div class=\"ve-ce-branchNode-slug ve-ce-branchNode-blockSlug\"><span class=\"oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-buttonElement oo-ui-buttonElement-frameless oo-ui-iconElement oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-buttonWidget\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><a class=\"oo-ui-buttonElement-button\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-disabled=\"false\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"oo-ui-iconElement-icon oo-ui-icon-add\"></span><span class=\"oo-ui-labelElement-label\">節を挿入</span><span class=\"oo-ui-indicatorElement-indicator oo-ui-indicatorElement-noIndicator\"></span></a></span></div><div style=\"padding-left: 2rem;\" id=\"mwvg\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><div class=\"ve-ce-branchNode-slug ve-ce-branchNode-blockSlug\"><span class=\"oo-ui-widget oo-ui-widget-enabled oo-ui-buttonElement oo-ui-buttonElement-frameless oo-ui-iconElement oo-ui-labelElement oo-ui-buttonWidget\" aria-disabled=\"false\"><a class=\"oo-ui-buttonElement-button\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-disabled=\"false\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"oo-ui-iconElement-icon oo-ui-icon-add\"></span><span class=\"oo-ui-labelElement-label\">節を挿入</span><span class=\"oo-ui-indicatorElement-indicator oo-ui-indicatorElement-noIndicator\"></span></a></span></div><dl id=\"mwvw\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><dt id=\"mwwA\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><p class=\"ve-ce-branchNode ve-ce-contentBranchNode ve-ce-paragraphNode ve-ce-generated-wrapper\"><code id=\"mwwQ\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-textStyleAnnotation ve-ce-codeAnnotation\">mawk</code> MBCS</p></dt><dd id=\"mwwg\" class=\"ve-ce-branchNode\"><p class=\"ve-ce-branchNode ve-ce-contentBranchNode ve-ce-paragraphNode ve-ce-generated-wrapper\">木村浩一（ハンドル名:Bruce）による<code id=\"mwww\" class=\"ve-ce-annotation ve-ce-textStyleAnnotat